^cbbGAME DIFFICULTIES

^C6fWhen you start the game, you are prompted to choose between four difficulties; 
the harder the difficulty, the stronger and more numerous the enemies. 
^P
^cbbGAME DIFFICULTIES		(cont'd.) 

^cccWHERE'S MY GRAVE?: ^c6fThis difficulty is only recommended for sissies and people 
with no FPS/PC gaming experience. Note: there is no enemy spawning on this difficulty, 
which eliminates a lot of the surprise/horror elements in the game.

^cccMAYBE JUST A SIP: ^c6fThis is a slightly better place for the inexperienced to 
start than the previous (mainly because we won't make fun of you AS MUCH for playing 
on this difficulty). Enemy spawning is left intact and certain enemies are stronger.


^P
^cbbGAME DIFFICULTIES		(cont'd.)

^cccRAVENOUS: ^c6fThis is the recommended difficulty setting. It provides a decent 
challenge even for experienced players.

^cccEVEN DEATH WILL BLEED: ^c6fIf you are a veteran player, someone who likes a good 
challenge, a masochist, or someone with suicidal tendencies, then this is a difficulty 
fit for you.       

